OL,7,FLess offshore decommissioning work was
OL,8,Fcarried out last year despite the
OL,9,Foverall amount of money being spent on
OL,10,Fthe activity increasing, the industry
OL,11,Fhas said.
OL,13,FOffshore Energy UK (OEUK) said #1.7
OL,14,Fbillion was spent on decommissioning
OL,15,Fin the UK continental shelf in 2023,
OL,16,Fup slightly from the previous year.
OL,18,FOEUK's annual offshore decommissioning
OL,19,Freport said only 126 wells were
OL,20,Fdecommissioned in 2023, compared to
OL,21,F139 in 2022.
