OL,4,Ccarried out in 2023 despite higher
OL,5,Cspend
OL,7,FMark Wilson, operations director at
OL,8,FOEUK, said: "Last year's report
OL,9,Fdiscussed the big challenges ahead,
OL,10,Ffrom the influx of renewable projects
OL,11,Fvying for the UK supply chain's
OL,12,Fresources, to the uncertain political
OL,13,Fand fiscal landscape that chilled
OL,14,Finvestment.
OL,16,F"The predicted upsurge in
OL,17,Fdecommissioning activity has landed,
OL,18,Feven if a damp squib: the spend has
OL,19,Frisen slightly in 2023 but activities
OL,20,Facross the decommissioning work
OL,21,Fbreakdown structure (WBS) have tumbled.
